[[印度尼西亚|印度尼西亚]]和[[荷兰|荷兰]]在1949年建立了外交关系。两国之间有着一种特殊的关系，<ref name="JakartaPost1">{{cite web|url=http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2012/04/02/indonesia-and-netherlands-a-special-relationship.html|title=Indonesia and the Netherlands: A special relationship|last=Marsudi|first=Retno|date=April 2, 2012|publisher=The Jakarta Post|access-date=29 May 2013|archive-date=2020-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812073151/https://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2012/04/02/indonesia-and-netherlands-a-special-relationship.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>这种关系植根于两国数百年来共同的[[殖民|殖民]]互动历史中。它开始于[[香料贸易|香料贸易]]期间，荷兰在现在的印度尼西亚建立了[[荷兰东印度公司|荷兰东印度公司]]贸易站，直到20世纪中期才被殖民为[[荷屬東印度群島|荷屬東印度群島]]。印度尼西亚是荷兰最大的前殖民地。在21世纪初，荷兰政府承诺加强与印尼的关系，指出经济、政治和人际交往应进一步加强。<ref name="JakartaPost2">{{cite web|url=http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2013/02/21/netherlands-put-new-emphasis-ties-with-indonesia.html|title=Netherlands to put new emphasis on ties with Indonesia|date=February 21, 2013|publisher=The Jakarta Post|access-date=29 May 2013|archive-date=2020-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812073153/https://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2013/02/21/netherlands-put-new-emphasis-ties-with-indonesia.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>
== 历史 ==
[[File:Stadhuis_Batavia,_Jakarta.jpg|thumb]]]]
1603年，荷兰东印度公司开始在现在的印度尼西亚开展业务，在那里它为了扩张业务而打了很多仗。<ref name=r29>Ricklefs, p.29</ref>虽然印尼历史上有其他欧洲殖民列强，但是荷兰巩固了他们对这个群岛的控制。1800年东印度公司破产后，1826年荷兰政府接管了群岛。<ref name="RICKLEFSp24">Ricklefs (1991), page 24</ref>在此之后，他们也与当地人作战，并强制执行了一段时间的强迫劳动和契约奴役，直到1870年。1901年，他们采纳了“荷兰伦理政策和印尼民族复兴政策”，其中包括对土著教育的投资有所增加和适度的政治改革。然而，直到20世纪，荷兰的统治才得到加强，成为后来的印度尼西亚。在[[第二次世界大战|第二次世界大战]]期间被[[日本|日本]]占领后，荷兰试图重新建立自己的统治，<ref>[http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/world/war/indo-inde.htm "Indonesian War of Independence"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/world/war/indo-inde.htm |date=20061210085210 }} Dutch wanted to reoccupy Indonesia</ref>在一场激烈的武装和外交斗争中，荷兰殖民最终于1949年12月结束。国际压力迫使荷兰正式承认印尼独立。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Bidien|first=Charles|date=5 December 1945|title=Independence the Issue|journal=Far Eastern Survey|volume=14|issue=24|pages=345–348|doi=10.1525/as.1945.14.24.01p17062|issn=0362-8949|jstor=3023219}}; {{cite web|url=http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/world/war/indo-inde.htm|title=Indonesian War of Independence|work=Military|publisher=GlobalSecurity.org|access-date=2006-12-11|archive-date=2006-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061210085210/http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/world/war/indo-inde.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>1956年，由[[苏加诺|苏加诺]]领导的印尼政府断绝了与荷兰的所有外交关系，直到1968年，[[新秩序_(印尼)|新秩序]]政府才恢复了这一关系。
== 高层互访 ==
[[File:Afscheid_Koninklijke_paar_op_vliegveld_van_Djakarta,_nr._Hare_Majesteit_en_Soeharto,_nr._10,_11,_12_Koninklijk_paar_zwaaiend_op_vliegtuigtrap.jpg|thumb]]
1970年，印度尼西亚总统[[苏哈托|苏哈托]]对荷兰进行正式访问，荷兰女王[[朱丽安娜女王|朱丽安娜]]和[[伯恩哈德王子_(利珀-比斯特费尔德)|王子伯恩哈德]]1971年对印度尼西亚进行了回访。<ref>{{cite web | title=State visit of Queen Juliana and Prince Bernhard to the Republic Indonesia in 1971 | url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kVEU3IhPIc4 | publisher=Dutch Docu Channel, via Youtube | access-date=May 20, 2014 | archive-date=2020-03-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200321032101/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kVEU3IhPIc4 | dead-url=no }}</ref>1995年，[[贝娅特丽克丝_(荷兰)|贝娅特丽克丝女王]]和[[克劳斯亲王_(荷兰)|克劳斯亲王]]也曾对印度尼西亚进行过皇室访问。<ref>{{cite web | title=Queen Beatrix and the former Dutch colonies | url=http://www.kitlv.nl/home/Spotlight?subpage_id=454 | publisher=KITLV | access-date=May 20, 2014 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140419140143/http://www.kitlv.nl/home/Spotlight?subpage_id=454 | archive-date=2014-04-19 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>2016年4月22日，[[佐科·维多多|佐科]]总统对荷兰进行正式访问。<ref>[https://apnews.com/b78f0f1fc1f74339af1d35ca7f02100b Indonesian President Joko Widodo visits Netherlands] {{Wayback|url=https://apnews.com/b78f0f1fc1f74339af1d35ca7f02100b |date=20200812071615 }} APnews. Published 22 April 2016</ref>2020年3月10日，[[威廉-亚历山大_(荷兰)|威廉-亚历山大国王]]对印度尼西亚进行了一次皇家访问，并出人意料地为印尼独立初期荷兰使用的过度暴力道歉。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://nltimes.nl/2020/03/10/dutch-king-apologizes-colonial-past-indonesia|title=Dutch King apologizes for colonial past in Indonesia|first=Janene|last=Pieters|date=10 March 2020|access-date=10 March 2020|work=NL Times|archive-date=2020-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200916090812/https://nltimes.nl/2020/03/10/dutch-king-apologizes-colonial-past-indonesia|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=BREAKING: Dutch monarch offers apology for past 'excessive violence'|url=https://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2020/03/10/breaking-dutch-monarch-offers-apology-for-past-excessive-violence.html|first=Marchio Irfan|last=Gorbiano|work=The Jakarta Post|date=10 March 2020|access-date=10 March 2020|archive-date=2020-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200625164405/https://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2020/03/10/breaking-dutch-monarch-offers-apology-for-past-excessive-violence.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>
== 政治关系 ==
[[自由巴布亚运动|自由巴布亚运动]]的分离主义意图破坏了两国之间的关系。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://webdiary.com.au/cms/?q=node%2F1408 |title=Papuan self-determination - historical roots VII {{!}} Webdiary - Founded and Inspired by Margo Kingston<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2021-08-18 |archive-date=2020-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200325190653/http://webdiary.com.au/cms/?q=node%2F1408 |dead-url=no }}</ref>此外，[[南马鲁古共和国|南马鲁古共和国]]也寻求从印度尼西亚独立出来。按照这种思路，他们曾在上世纪70年代和80年代袭击过荷兰的目标，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.safecom.org.au/dutch-moluccans.htm |title=Moluccans in the Netherlands: a snapshot about Refugees in Holland<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2021-03-29 |archive-date=2020-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812063749/http://www.safecom.org.au/dutch-moluccans.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>试图迫使荷兰向印尼施压，允许其国家脱离印尼。当时，两国政治关系紧张，因为印尼官员拒绝访问荷兰，而这群人被允许向法庭提起诉讼。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rnw.nl/english/bulletin/rms-issue-frustrates-dutch-indonesian-relations |title=RMS issue frustrates Dutch-Indonesian relations {{!}} Radio Netherlands Worldwide<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2010-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140325165059/http://www.rnw.nl/english/bulletin/rms-issue-frustrates-dutch-indonesian-relations |archive-date=2014-03-25 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>然而，荷兰外交部长于2005年访问印尼，庆祝印尼独立60周年，荷兰称这“标志着两国关系的一个历史性时刻”。在这次访问之后，印度尼西亚和荷兰之间的关系因在广泛领域扩大合作而进一步加强和加强。”<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.minbuza.nl/PostenWeb/I/Indonesi%C3%AB/Netherlands_Embassy_in_Jakarta/the_Embassy/Departments/Political_Affairs |title=Political Affairs - Netherlands Embassy in Jakarta<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2010-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101201154138/http://www.minbuza.nl/PostenWeb/I/Indonesi%C3%AB/Netherlands_Embassy_in_Jakarta/the_Embassy/Departments/Political_Affairs |archive-date=2010-12-01 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

2010年，印尼总统[[苏西洛·班邦·尤多约诺|苏西洛·班邦·尤多约诺]]取消了对荷兰的访问，因为该组织的活动人士要求荷兰法庭对他发出逮捕令。.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/asia-pacific/2010/10/2010105131324456865.html|title=Indonesia leader delays Dutch visit|website=www.aljazeera.com|access-date=2019-09-28|archive-date=2020-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812063603/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/asia-pacific/2010/10/2010105131324456865.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>这一举动受到了[[雅加达|雅加达]]亲印尼的[[摩鹿加人|摩鹿加]]活动人士的谴责。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.itnsource.com/shotlist/RTV/2010/10/07/RTV2558110/?v=0&a=1|title=INDONESIA: Group of pro-government activists protest against rivals seeking the arrest of President Susilo Bambang Yudhoyono|website=www.gettyimages.co.uk|access-date=2019-09-28|archive-date=2016-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161113114823/http://www.itnsource.com/shotlist/RTV/2010/10/07/RTV2558110/?v=0&a=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>

